  "notes": [
    "Source: IRremoteESP8266 (github.com/crankyoldgit/IRremoteESP8266) — ir_LG.h/.cpp, MIT license.",
    "Remote model: AKB73757604 (split inverter). Korean lineup: AMNW24GTPA1 / A4UW30GFA2 듀얼 인버터 split AC.",
    "Protocol: LG2 (28-bit). 28-bit LG AC packet = [0x88 sign | Power(2b) | reserved(3b) | Mode(3b) | (Temp-15)(4b) | Fan(4b) | Sum(4b)].",
    "주의: lg-ac-akb73757604.json (NEC 32-bit) 은 같은 리모컨 번호이지만 LG의 휴대용/창문형 AC 변종입니다. 이 파일은 split(벽걸이) 인버터용입니다.",
    "All state commands are computed using IRremoteESP8266's encoder. mode_*, temp_*, fan_* defaults: COOL mode @ 24°C with fan-auto.",
    "Toggle/sub commands (power_off, light_toggle, swing_v_*, swing_h_*) are literal IRremoteESP8266 constants.",
    "AKB73757604 is the only LG remote in this catalog that supports horizontal swing (swing_h_auto / swing_h_off).",
    "power_on sends the standard COOL/24°C/auto state packet — modern LG ACs treat any state with Power=ON as a power-on command.",
    "Carrier: 38 kHz."
  ],
